Loading data - merging sheets

sheet <- excel_sheets(data/_raw/project_data_raw.xlsx)

data_frame <- lapply(setNames(sheet, sheet), function(x) read_excel(data/_raw/project_data_raw.xlsx, sheet = x))

data_frame <- bind_rows(data_frame, .id = “Sheet”)
